title: Sara Doorsoun
summary: Sara Doorsoun-Khajeh (Persian: سارا دورسون خواجه, Turkish: Sara Dursun; born 17 November 1991) is a German footballer who plays as a defender for Eintracht Frankfurt and the German national team. She previously played for Wattenscheid 09, Bad Neuenahr, Turbine Potsdam, SGS Essen, VfL Wolfsburg and Eintracht Frankfurt.
